***we use python3 so make sure to make it default
run "sudo update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/python python /usr/bin/python3 10"

***if you get an OS:error such as: "OSError: libespeak.so.1: cannot open shared object file: No such file or directory"
run "sudo apt-get update && sudo apt-get install espeak"

***to fix "[CRITICAL] [App         ] Unable to get a Window, abort."
run "sudo apt-get install libsdl2-2.0-0 libsdl2-image-2.0-0 libsdl2-mixer-2.0-0 libsdl2-ttf-2.0-0"

***to fix pyAudio problems such as "ERROR: Failed building wheel for PyAudio"
run "sudo apt install libasound-dev portaudio19-dev libportaudiocpp0"
